rows.label: qst003104_msg0001
rows.name:
You'll help us with our
supply operations?

rows.label: qst003104_msg0003
rows.name: We're short of fish-based meals here.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0004
rows.name:
If you could make a few fishy
dishes and bring them to us, that
would really ease the burden.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0005
rows.name: Thanks a lot for your assistance!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0006
rows.name:
Our services have been a
bit strained since the
Acedian refugees arrived.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0007
rows.name:
Us soldiers are stretched to the
absolute limit here, already.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0008
rows.name:
Honestly, having to worry about all
these refugees on top of it all is
just about pushing us over the edge.

rows.label: qst003104_msg0009
rows.name:
But you lot have really
eased up the burden!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0010
rows.name:
I think we've got a much
better chance of helping out
all these needy people now!

rows.label: qst003104_msg0011
rows.name:
Thank you so much!
We're indebted to you!
